有孩子  视频  推特
They have their children, their videos, their Twitter.

362
00:23:15,420 --> 00:23:18,230
没几个人理解我们
There are very few people who understand us.

363
00:23:18,230 --> 00:23:20,440
密查姆就是一个
Meechum... was one.

364
00:23:22,510 --> 00:23:23,730
