371
00:24:18,120 --> 00:24:19,960
-我要叫警察了  -好了  好了
- I'm calling the cops. - All right, all right.

372
00:24:19,960 --> 00:24:22,000
-马上叫警察  -好了  好了
- The cops, right now... - All right, all right.

373
00:24:22,000 --> 00:24:23,490
-我要叫警察  -好了  好了
- I'm calling the cops. - All right, all right.

374
00:24:28,580 --> 00:24:29,450
女士
Ma'am...

375
00:24:32,940 --> 00:24:34,200
