I'm Officer Tom.

376
00:24:38,410 --> 00:24:39,480
是您打的电话吗
You called for me?

377
00:24:42,460 --> 00:24:44,420
刚刚有个人
There was a man here.

378
00:24:45,720 --> 00:24:48,450
