在这儿见过这个坏人吗
Did you ever see this bad man on your block?

382
00:25:00,620 --> 00:25:02,740
在这儿见过这个坏人吗
Did you ever see this bad man on your block?

383
00:25:06,690 --> 00:25:07,540
好吧
All right.

384
00:25:08,600 --> 00:25:11,870
那这个女人呢  见过她吗
What about this woman? Did you ever see her?

385
